4. **Settings page**: Navigate to Settings → Appearance. All three named themes are shown as radio
   buttons. Selecting one updates the whole UI. The footer shows the theme name.
5. **Backward compat**: Components that use `resolvedTheme` (`DiffPanel`, `ChatMarkdown`,
   `DiffWorkerPoolProvider`) continue to work unchanged because the new hook still exports
   `resolvedTheme: "light" | "dark"` derived from `theme.colorScheme`.
6. **Old localStorage values**: Clear storage or set `t3code:theme` to `"system"` manually —
   the app should silently fall back to `"t3-dark"` without errors.

